<h1>Register New Person</h1>

<p>System administrators can register new person for the radiology information system.</p>
<p>Clicking the "<span class="code">+Person</span>" hyperlink will directe system administrators to the New Person Register page.</p>

<p>You need to provide the following information:</p>

<ul>
	<li>First Name</li>
	<li>Last Name</li>
	<li>Address</li>
	<li>Email*</li>
	<li>Phone</li>
	<li>Password</li>
</ul>

<p><span class="code">* Note that the Email should be unique, which means that a person cannot have the same Email with any other perseon in our database.</span></p>

<p>Click the "<span class="code">Add</span>" button to register. Click the "<span class="code">cancel</span>" button to cancel the registration.</p>

